SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK b1 WITH FRAME TITLE TEXT-001.

“— Task List Type (At least one must be selected)
SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF LINE.
SELECTION-SCREEN COMMENT 1(30) TEXT-t01.
SELECTION-SCREEN END OF LINE.

PARAMETERS: p_functloc AS CHECKBOX DEFAULT ‘X’ USER-COMMAND utype,
p_equip    AS CHECKBOX USER-COMMAND utype,
p_gen      AS CHECKBOX USER-COMMAND utype.

SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK b1.

