- Selection Texts
  *–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––*
- TEXT-001: Task List Type
- TEXT-t01: Task List Type (at least one required)
- TEXT-002: Task List Selection
- TEXT-003: Header Data
- TEXT-004: Operation Data
- TEXT-005: Characteristic Data
- TEXT-006: Detailed View
